    "name": "Red Mantis Assassin Dedication",
    "prerequisite": "trained in *sawtooth sabers*; worshipper of *Achaekek*; member of the Red Mantis assassins",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You have learned how to stalk your foes and slay them with a sawtooth saber. You become trained in Stealth and Assassin Lore; if you were already trained, you become an expert instead. Whenever your proficiency in any weapon increases to expert or beyond, you also gain that new proficiency with sawtooth sabers.  \n  \n You become bound by Achaekek's anathema and can receive his sanctification.",
